name: I_know_myself
description: Videoart, 6:04min ,1024 x 1024. This video artwork has been created to collaborate with the Trans Collective. The money collected will be used to contribute with the mastectomy of Gabriel Vicente Torres ,who as many others, has been fighting for the Transgender Collective claims. This video explores the use of Deep Learning technologies to reflect the fluidity of pre-established concepts as gender of the Cyborg century. The sound has been also composed with algorithmic tools on Pure Data to be fully coherent in the creative process.
